latestPosts.caption:
Meet Our Co-Founder And The Journey Behind Rosa Amoris. 

Every luxury brand has its origin story, and Rosa Amoris is no different. Adeesh Nahar, Co-founder & Director, shares how the brand evolved from its roots, drawing inspiration from timeless elegance while adapting to changing design styles and preferences over the years. Rosa Amoris embraces this evolution, offering creations that reflect the perfect balance of tradition and contemporary luxury.

#RosaAmoris #LuxuryWithPurpose #EleganceUnveiled

The Vision Behind Rosa Amoris: Redefining Jewellery

Adeesh Nahar, Co-founder & Director of Rosa Amoris, discusses how the brand is transforming the jewellery landscape. With an unwavering commitment to innovation, craftsmanship, and timeless beauty, Rosa Amoris is shaping the future of luxury jewellery, one masterpiece at a time.

#RosaAmoris #LuxuryRedefined #TimelessCraftsmanship #JewelleryWithPurpose

Redefining Luxury: The Rosa Amoris Journey
Built on a foundation of extensive research and impeccable craftsmanship, Rosa Amoris embodies luxury, elegance, and timeless design.

In this exclusive insight, Adeesh Nahar, Co-founder & Director, shares the vision behind the brand and how it continues to set new benchmarks in India’s high jewellery landscape.

#RosaAmoris #TimelessElegance #LuxuryRedefined

latestPosts.caption:
An embodiment of universal equilibrium, the ensemble plays with visual illusions and parametric tessellations to mirror the delicate balance of time. On Avantika, it becomes a portrait of quiet strength— grounded in symmetry, yet fluid in spirit.

The timeless yet contemporary silhouette is elevated by our three-dimensional lamina scale embroidery, adding striking textural depth. As the design landscape evolves, its transformative power celebrates authenticity— where couture becomes an extension of the beauty that resides within you.

latestPosts.caption:
Inspired by the Hindu philosophy of reincarnation, we reimagine pre-loved vintage Banarsi sarees into modern, structured drapes. Every creation is a symbol of eternity—revived through our signature cording techniques and molded into silhouettes that honour its soul while embracing a new form.

Avantika Vandanapu (avantika) reflects the timeless grace of Banarsi craftsmanship. Much like her, it stands rooted in tradition, yet remains effortlessly contemporary—honouring heritage while evolving for the present.

Styling: Daniel Franklin (@dhfranklin)
Photography: Nishanth Radhakrishnan (@nishanth.radhakrishnan)
Videography: Nirvair Singh Rai (@nirvairrai)

A study in duality—where organic form fuses with engineered textile.
Avantika Vandanapu (avantika) embodies the pulse of heritage, with our signature materials hand-embroidered into a bespoke creation that seamlessly blends traditional techniques with innovative craftsmanship.
Where rhythmic motion meets sculpted stillness, 
she channels both strength and grace.
On her, it becomes a story of evolution.

Photography: Nishanth Radhakrishnan (@nishanth.radhakrishnan)
